      "Text": "Security update for pdns-recursor",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for pdns-recursor fixes the following issues:\n\nSecurity issues fixed:\n\n- CVE-2018-10851: Fixed denial of service via crafted zone record or crafted answer (bsc#1114157).\n- CVE-2018-14644: Fixed denial of service via crafted query for meta-types (bsc#1114170).\n- CVE-2018-14626: Fixed packet cache pollution via crafted query (bsc#1114169).\n- CVE-2018-16855: Fixed case where a crafted query could cause a denial of service (bsc#1116592)\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
    },
